languages.text: Старший Блюститель: "Мы совершили аварийный прыжок в варп, едва успели запустить поле Геллера и направляемся Трон знает куда, ведомые неизвестной силой! Леди-Навигатор и Лорд-капитан до сих пор не обнаружены. Расскажи. Мне. Еще раз. Что произошло в Санктум Навис?"

languages.text: Senior Enforcer: "We performed an emergency warp jump, barely activated the Geller field in time, and are now being dragged to Throne knows where by an unknown force! The Lady Navigator and the Lord Captain are still unaccounted for. Now tell me. One. More. Time. What transpired in the Sanctum Navis?"

languages.text: 上級エンフォーサー：「我々は緊急ワープジャンプを実行し、どうにか時間内にゲラーフィールドを起動させたら、今度は未知の力で玉座が知る場所へと引きずり出されている！航宙士殿とロード・キャプテンからの説明はまだない。さあ話せ。もう一度、聞くぞ。サンクトゥム・ネイヴィスで何が起きた？」
languages.original_text: Senior Enforcer: "We performed an emergency warp jump, barely activated the Geller field in time, and are now being dragged to Throne knows where by an unknown force! The Lady Navigator and the Lord Captain are still unaccounted for. Now tell me. One. More. Time. What transpired in the Sanctum Navis?"

languages.text: 高阶执法者：“我们进行了紧急亚空间跳跃，勉强及时启动了盖勒力场。目前，我们正被某种未知的力量拖走。至于要拖到哪里，恐怕只有黄金王座才知道了！导航者女士与领主舰长仍然下落不明。我、再、问、一、遍。当时，导航者圣所里到底发生了什么事情？”
languages.original_text: Senior Enforcer: "We performed an emergency warp jump, barely activated the Geller field in time, and are now being dragged to Throne knows where by an unknown force! The Lady Navigator and the Lord Captain are still unaccounted for. Now tell me. One. More. Time. What transpired in the Sanctum Navis?"

languages.text: Prévôt supérieur : « Nous avons à peine eu le temps d'activer le champ de Geller avant de faire un saut d'urgence dans le Warp, et maintenant une force inconnue nous entraîne le Trône seul sait où ! La dame navigatrice et {mf|le seigneur-capitaine|la seigneure-capitaine} sont toujours {mf|portés disparus|portées disparues}. Alors. Encore. Une. Fois. Que s'est-il passé dans le sanctum navis ? »
languages.original_text: Senior Enforcer: "We performed an emergency warp jump, barely activated the Geller field in time, and are now being dragged to Throne knows where by an unknown force! The Lady Navigator and the Lord Captain are still unaccounted for. Now tell me. One. More. Time. What transpired in the Sanctum Navis?"

traits.locale_text: Prévôt supérieur : « Nous avons à peine eu le temps d'activer le champ Geller avant de faire un saut d'urgence dans le Warp, et maintenant une force inconnue nous entraîne le Trône seul sait où ! La dame navigatrice et {mf|le seigneur-capitaine|la seigneure-capitaine} sont toujours {mf|portés disparus|portées disparues}. Alors. Encore. Une. Fois. Que s'est-il passé dans le sanctum navis ? »

languages.text: Jefe de guardias: «¡Efectuamos un salto de disformidad de emergencia, activamos el campo Geller por los pelos, y ahora una fuerza desconocida nos arrastra el Trono sabe adónde! La lady Navegante y {mf|el|la} Lord Capitán siguen en paradero desconocido. Ahora cuéntamelo. Una. Vez. Más. ¿Qué ocurrió en el Sanctum Navis?».
languages.original_text: Senior Enforcer: "We performed an emergency warp jump, barely activated the Geller field in time, and are now being dragged to Throne knows where by an unknown force! The Lady Navigator and the Lord Captain are still unaccounted for. Now tell me. One. More. Time. What transpired in the Sanctum Navis?"

traits.locale_text: Jefe de guardias: «¡Efectuamos un salto de emergencia a la disformidad, activamos el campo Geller por los pelos, y ahora una fuerza desconocida nos arrastra el Trono sabe adónde! La lady Navegante y {mf|el|la} Lord Capitán siguen en paradero desconocido. Ahora cuéntamelo. Una. Vez. Más. ¿Qué ocurrió en el Sanctum Navis?».

languages.text: Senior Enforcer: "Wir haben einen Notfall-Warpsprung ausgeführt, das Gellerfeld gerade noch rechtzeitig aktiviert und werden nun von Thron weiß welcher unbekannten Macht geschleppt! Die Lady Navigator und der Lord Captain sind noch immer verschwunden. Und nun frage ich. Ein. Letztes. Mal. Was ist im Sanctum Navis geschehen?"
languages.original_text: Senior Enforcer: "We performed an emergency warp jump, barely activated the Geller field in time, and are now being dragged to Throne knows where by an unknown force! languages.text: Kıdemli İnfazcı: "Acil durum öte sıçraması yaptık, Geller alanını az kalsın etkinleştiremiyorduk, şimdi de bilinmeyen bir güç bizi Taht bilir nerelere sürüklüyor! Leydi Rotacı'yla Lord Kaptan'ın akıbeti hâlâ muallakta. Şimdi. Tekrar anlat bakalım. Navis Kutağı'nda ne yaşandı?"
